Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.00,0:01:36.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託了 拓海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.77,0:01:40.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這事實在太丟臉 沒法告訴健二他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.44,0:01:45.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我覺得不說的話你又不能理解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.75,0:01:49.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我覺得很不愉快 不能原諒那女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.06,0:01:50.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拓海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.12,0:01:56.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別把真子想那麼壞 她是個好女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.01,0:01:59.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼前輩要袒護那女人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.80,0:02:03.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不明白 前輩你沒必要做到這個份上吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.95,0:02:07.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託了 拓海 請你理解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.17,0:02:17.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了 拓海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.85,0:02:21.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是第一次來秋名以外的山道吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.53,0:02:23.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼樣? 能跑嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.04,0:02:26.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那種事不跑怎麼知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.42,0:02:37.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會去跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.45,0:02:39.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.37,0:02:42.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉 承你恩情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.88,0:02:48.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然無法理解前輩和那女人是什麼情況...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.47,0:02:49.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拓海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.57,0:02:53.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之我會開86去碓冰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.90,0:03:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\pos(147,116)\fs20\fad(650,750)}驟死賽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.87,0:03:05.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的嗎? 健二前輩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.15,0:03:09.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拓海那小子要和碓冰山道的Sil-80比賽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.64,0:03:11.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難以置信啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.07,0:03:13.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.78,0:03:19.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他應該不是那種主動跑去別的山道比賽的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.64,0:03:22.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,池谷前輩是怎麼拜託他的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.42,0:03:24.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不太清楚啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.14,0:03:28.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,詳情池谷那小子沒告訴我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.70,0:03:31.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以前他曾說過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.74,0:03:36.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒在秋名以外跑過的拓海 在別的山道會有何表現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.46,0:03:41.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道不理解那想見識一下的心情嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.50,0:03:46.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可也不能馬上就和當地最快的Sil-80比賽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.48,0:03:49.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拓海要去碓冰比賽?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.43,0:03:51.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊 店長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.92,0:03:54.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對方的Sil-80有那麼厲害?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.79,0:03:57.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經不是厲害的問題了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.56,0:04:00.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那狹窄的碓冰道路上自由自在地賣弄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.08,0:04:03.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連假動作都用上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.90,0:04:09.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拓海也一起看過那Sil-80 不可能不知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.77,0:04:11.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但拓海的話會贏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.70,0:04:13.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總是像你這麼樂觀可真好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.06,0:04:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當地也無人能贏 加油站的小哥不也這麼說過嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.30,0:04:19.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說不定拓海...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.15,0:04:23.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從一開始就將勝負置之度外而去比賽的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.61,0:04:36.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦? 不好 抽光了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.75,0:04:40.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開86去買點吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.40,0:04:48.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼情況?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.23,0:04:51.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,86變85了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.35,0:04:55.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,車借一下 留這個代替
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.99,0:05:07.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在你老爸肯定在驚訝吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.70,0:05:11.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,86不知何時變成了我的85
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.89,0:05:17.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,池谷 有件事想問你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.46,0:05:18.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.76,0:05:21.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天的比賽你幫哪一邊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.70,0:05:25.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,問我幫哪邊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.73,0:05:28.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是比賽的中間人 兩不相幫...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.30,0:05:32.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這話當真?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.66,0:05:36.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想過拓海的立場嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.05,0:05:39.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你小子是不是光顧著真子的漂亮臉蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.91,0:05:41.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,眼裏已經容不下朋友了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.25,0:05:43.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪有這回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.54,0:05:44.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 有的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.56,0:05:50.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那告訴我 你覺得拓海有勝算嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.07,0:05:54.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼樣? 池谷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.71,0:05:56.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明確回答我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.29,0:06:00.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.04,0:06:06.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可能贏的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.99,0:06:09.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只熟悉秋名山道的拓海...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.39,0:06:11.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在生平第一次跑的碓冰...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.95,0:06:13.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那麼困難的賽道上...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.04,0:06:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然那小子技術超群
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.82,0:06:21.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但也有憑技術無法解決的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.24,0:06:24.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是賽道熟悉程度的問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.07,0:06:27.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,練習也沒有就直接動真格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.48,0:06:29.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算是拓海也毫無勝算
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.49,0:06:34.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不可能連這個都不清楚吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.19,0:06:36.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.87,0:06:40.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是 所有男人對自己喜歡的女人都很軟弱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.12,0:06:47.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作為車手日子裏最後夏天的回憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.07,0:06:51.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請讓我和秋名的86在碓冰山道比賽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.78,0:06:56.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但你別做出為討好女人而出賣朋友的舉動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.20,0:07:01.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你忘了拓海和86在最困難的時候幫過你嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.04,0:07:04.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,秋名的86是我們的驕傲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.31,0:07:08.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種比賽可以放棄了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.90,0:07:09.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不然...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.01,0:07:12.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就和你絕交
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.31,0:07:27.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,健二 明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.02,0:07:34.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.72,0:07:40.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該更早點和你商量的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.21,0:07:43.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過我一個人考慮了很久...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.46,0:07:46.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.53,0:07:48.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼不做車手?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.37,0:07:56.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兩年前 剛開始飆車時快樂得忘乎所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.15,0:08:00.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一直以本地第一作為目標
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.83,0:08:05.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在也很快樂 不是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.11,0:08:12.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼說呢 現在沒有了那時候的緊張感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.77,0:08:15.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也不知道是怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.70,0:08:20.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我覺得差不多是時候了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.65,0:08:28.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到此為止就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.64,0:08:34.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎? 不說清楚讓我很不痛快啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.46,0:08:37.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想交個男朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.77,0:08:40.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嘗試一下像沙雪這樣普通的戀愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.27,0:08:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我覺得車手也一樣能交到男朋友啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.50,0:08:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行啊 我想沙雪你不會明白我的感受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.30,0:08:52.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你其實有了喜歡的男人了吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.87,0:09:16.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我坦白 有個人我思慕了很久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.08,0:09:19.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我都不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.17,0:09:21.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是瞎猜的 這事還是第一次聽到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.48,0:09:25.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想沙雪你也不會明白的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.57,0:09:31.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他不是附近的人 只是我單方面地遠距離思慕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.25,0:09:37.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那算什麼 該說你是少女情趣還是晚熟?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.82,0:09:39.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都二十歲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.97,0:09:44.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什麼關係 只是思慕著就滿足了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.01,0:09:46.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是思慕?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.19,0:09:49.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你必須面對現實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.96,0:09:50.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.54,0:09:56.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可我和沙雪這兩年的持續努力究竟到了什麼程度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.76,0:10:00.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想在最後的比賽中驗證一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.64,0:10:02.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,意味著告別過去呢...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.27,0:10:07.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對你來說很不錯 完全夠格做真子的對手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.45,0:10:12.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是醜話說在前面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.69,0:10:14.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在碓冰山道比賽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.51,0:10:17.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管對手是誰 輸了的話是絕不能原諒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.48,0:10:21.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不然的話我絕不同意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.43,0:10:23.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.43,0:10:27.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們是非贏不可的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.05,0:10:30.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算對手是秋名86
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.11,0:10:33.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,絕對可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.40,0:10:42.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是這麼回事 不想比賽的話別勉強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.17,0:10:45.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我和池谷會和對方說清楚的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.19,0:10:47.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在下個出口回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.45,0:10:52.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就這麼辦吧 麻煩你了 拓海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.22,0:10:55.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原諒他吧 拓海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.63,0:10:59.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,健二前輩 我不想回去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.04,0:11:01.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拓海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.10,0:11:04.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想比賽才去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.71,0:11:09.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是我自己的意志 沒打算過要回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.05,0:11:11.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拓海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.44,0:11:15.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是拓海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.87,0:11:18.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也見過真子的實力 應該明白吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.97,0:11:20.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼想也太不合算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.79,0:11:24.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算是你也沒有勝算
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.43,0:11:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.25,0:11:28.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,勝負對我來說無所謂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.85,0:11:30.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼可以 你別說得那麼輕鬆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.05,0:11:34.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說到秋名86 現在可是轟動一時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.51,0:11:36.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你應該自重點才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.65,0:11:41.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不太擅長那樣 碰巧都在本地所以才贏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.61,0:11:46.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虛名在外的話感覺很難受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.11,0:11:51.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那種傳聞早點消散反而更痛快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.59,0:11:53.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼會...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.35,0:11:55.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.54,0:12:01.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只想在第一次跑的山道上盡情挑戰一番而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.92,0:12:09.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思 池谷 剛才說得太過份了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.93,0:12:13.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,經拓海那麼一說 我們也沒話好說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.42,0:12:19.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拓海真是個不可思議的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.92,0:12:22.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,該說他是和我們想法不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.89,0:12:25.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是實力過人的表現呢...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.96,0:12:27.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難以理解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.84,0:12:44.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,輪胎沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.55,0:12:48.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這種山道情況下最有抓地力的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.18,0:12:51.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,懸掛也不用改
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.16,0:12:52.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,照現在這樣就是最棒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.15,0:12:55.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沙雪說的絕不會錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.65,0:12:56.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想你也應該明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.30,0:13:01.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真正比賽時不能用大角度的漂移
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.86,0:13:06.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有可滑和不可滑彎道的靈活運用也是關鍵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.48,0:13:10.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特別是在這連續彎較多的碓冰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.81,0:13:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有我在 你只要相信自己的技術全力前進就行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.12,0:13:16.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會輸給任何人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.11,0:13:22.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下定決心了 包在我身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.46,0:13:24.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為我們是二位一體的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.62,0:13:27.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我熱血沸騰了 沙雪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.78,0:13:30.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今晚展現出迄今為止的最強跑法吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.78,0:13:32.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好期待哦 真興奮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.71,0:13:34.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會是場什麼樣的比賽?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.36,0:13:36.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會是個什麼樣的對手?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.10,0:14:00.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拓海 怎麼才能取勝?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.24,0:14:03.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什麼戰術? 告訴我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.92,0:14:05.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.58,0:14:08.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那算什麼 什麼辦法都沒有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.22,0:14:11.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不想看到你輸啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.35,0:14:23.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.04,0:14:26.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,碓冰很狹窄 也沒什麼直路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.80,0:14:30.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以呢...搶跑一點佔住先機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.16,0:14:33.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這算什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.33,0:14:35.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後就堵在路中間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.64,0:14:38.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不讓她超車地跑下去 不就贏了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.91,0:14:42.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那樣太卑鄙了 不可能這麼做吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.78,0:14:46.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可讓她佔了先機甩開的話就輸了吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.95,0:14:48.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,話說的沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.27,0:14:55.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒什麼好的戰術嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.68,0:14:58.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家都是裝了四個輪胎的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.98,0:15:17.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真是86的車手!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.76,0:15:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有點難以置信 你幾歲了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.43,0:15:23.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,十八了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.55,0:15:28.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,十八...高中生...饒了我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.84,0:15:31.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們也才二十而已 我覺得也夠年輕的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.54,0:15:32.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且還是女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.48,0:15:37.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,年紀小的話就更加不能輸了 真子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.25,0:15:52.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就切入正題吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.17,0:15:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比賽的方法是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.70,0:16:02.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,並排起步的方法不太適合這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.15,0:16:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為出發後搶得先機的人就完全佔了上風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.94,0:16:09.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像這樣狡猾地比誰搶跑快的比賽令人厭惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.74,0:16:12.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個戰術不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.32,0:16:13.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那...怎麼比?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.61,0:16:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先行後追的比賽 明白嗎? 就是追逐賽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.82,0:16:21.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先行者將後追者甩開就算贏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.35,0:16:26.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無法甩開的話再互換位置 直到決出勝負為止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.11,0:16:29.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是驟死賽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.65,0:16:30.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.82,0:16:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.59,0:16:37.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們是主場 所以第一輪位置的選擇權在你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.72,0:16:39.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,決定前後吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.81,0:16:42.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.83,0:16:44.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來這邊 拓海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.01,0:16:50.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種規則的話 第一輪肯定選先行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.52,0:16:53.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為能確保拖延到第二輪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.67,0:16:55.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且有一輪可以練習
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.61,0:16:58.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第二輪輸了也沒那麼難看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.73,0:17:01.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正第一輪對方會選先行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.96,0:17:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在第二輪決勝負 別擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.68,0:17:08.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難得大家費心建議 但不好意思...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.01,0:17:13.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前輩 我不喜歡那樣做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.62,0:17:15.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在說什麼啊 拓海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.46,0:17:18.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第一輪我從後面出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.24,0:17:18.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.40,0:17:21.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再想想清楚 拓海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.19,0:17:25.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是我的比賽 我自己會決定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.57,0:17:27.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.54,0:17:31.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從後面出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.06,0:17:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,後面?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.67,0:17:38.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他到底是囂張還是笨蛋?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.99,0:17:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也好 甩開他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.61,0:17:59.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰啊 空不出手啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.00,0:18:03.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏是藤原豆腐店
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.07,0:18:05.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 文太嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.76,0:18:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了 是你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.60,0:18:09.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.85,0:18:11.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有件事我很關心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.11,0:18:13.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實是拓海那小子...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.67,0:18:17.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,差不多了 要開始啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.50,0:18:20.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去碓冰山道比賽?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.89,0:18:21.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦 這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.73,0:18:24.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,「哦 這樣啊」你要說的就這些?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.36,0:18:26.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不擔心嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.46,0:18:30.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,擔心什麼 他可是我兒子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.84,0:18:33.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們會慢慢出發 別心急 跟在後面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.34,0:18:38.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,過了第一個彎就會全力加速衝刺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.66,0:18:40.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是比賽開始的信號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.03,0:19:03.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就這些 沒別的了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.67,0:19:06.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就這些 我很忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.08,0:19:08.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒什麼事就別打電話來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.87,0:19:10.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,文太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.50,0:19:20.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拓海 我是個笨蛋 到現在才醒悟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.89,0:19:22.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我應該明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.06,0:19:25.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你為了我的面子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.65,0:19:27.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早知會輸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.06,0:19:29.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卻還是接受了這種無理的比賽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.44,0:19:32.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我現在非常後悔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.14,0:19:38.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你可是我們所有秋名車手的驕傲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.01,0:19:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我做了無法挽回的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.17,0:19:51.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不想看到你這樣不明不白地輸掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.15,0:19:53.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拓海不會輸的 前輩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.99,0:19:57.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說是這麼說 但現實是殘酷的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.18,0:20:00.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我的錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.69,0:20:01.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,池谷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.03,0:20:09.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前輩 我是考慮過了才選後追的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.32,0:20:09.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.07,0:20:14.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖不知能否取勝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.61,0:20:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我從一開始就沒想過要輸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.33,0:20:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拓海 有什麼戰術?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.66,0:20:25.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,談不上什麼戰術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.98,0:20:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是非常單純的想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.58,0:20:30.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼想法? 拓海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.77,0:20:32.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,告訴我們吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.85,0:20:37.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無論對方的車有多快 也不可能飛上天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.88,0:20:42.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,同樣都是車子 裝了四個輪胎的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.23,0:20:46.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以 對方能轉的彎道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.42,0:20:50.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我應該也能用同樣的速度來轉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.38,0:20:52.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是這樣想的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.82,0:20:55.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.41,0:20:58.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,理論上是沒錯...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.85,0:21:00.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那也太亂來了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.38,0:21:02.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要出發了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.90,0:21:11.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 上吧 真子 一輪就結束這場比賽吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.28,0:21:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 沙雪 展現出迄今為止的最強跑法吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.91,0:22:00.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兩車都是全油門跑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.57,0:22:02.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,終於開始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.26,0:22:04.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拓海的第一次客場比賽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.11,0:22:07.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是 就算是拓海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.37,0:22:10.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比賽的條件也太過艱難
